      • mergeWorkingSets

        boolean mergeWorkingSets(User user,
                       WorkingSet firstWorkingSet,
                       java.util.List<WorkingSet> wss,
                       boolean deleteRemains)
        Merge two or more working sets into first working set if mergeToFirst is set to true.
        If Set of WSs are merged, then content of WSs will be added to WS1.
        If mergeToFirst is set to false, the Wss will be merged to the current working set
        Set {WSs - WS1} will be deleted if deleteRemains is set to true

        Parameters:
        user -
        wss -
        boolean -
        boolean -
        Returns:
        boolean
        See Also:
        User, WorkingSet
